# Russian translations for slint-replay (overlay-host binary).
#
# IMPORTANT: gettext matches by EXACT English msgid. When a @tr("…")
# string changes in any ui/*.slint file, the matching msgid here must be
# updated in lockstep or the lookup silently falls back to English.
# This file was FULLY re-synced in Phase E6 cycle 38 against the live
# @tr() set in overlay_bar / tile / palette / settings_panel (the old
# extraction had drifted across ~35 UI cycles, which is why Russian
# "was selected but not actually there").
#
# Wrapped surfaces:
# - ui/overlay_bar.slint
# - ui/tile.slint
# - ui/palette.slint
# - ui/settings_panel.slint

